    {
      "id": "1ab4750c-f3ba-8047-b6c5-e90c62859c89",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Experiments using a randomized experiment test whether learners who engaged with eDoer acquired more knowledge than those who did not. While interacting with the system seems to lead to better scores, there is not significant different between students who received personalized recommendations vs those who did not.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
